text: You Can't Have Everything is a 1937 American musical movie directed by Norman Taurog and starring Alice Faye, Don Ameche, Al Ritz, Jimmy Ritz, Harry Ritz, Gypsy Rose Lee. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1937 movies Category:1930s American musical movies Category:Movies directed by Norman Taurog
